<div class="container">
  <div class="row m-5 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col text-center">
      <h3><strong>本当に退会しますか？</strong></h3>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col text-center">
      <p>
